editorialNotes.tagline: Get around with a Quebec favourite
editorialNotes.standard: Whether you’re commuting to work, or hopping a metro in a new city, Transit is your indispensable guide to public transit systems, car- and bike-share services, and more. In addition to live trip-planning updates, Transit will tell you when to leave and give exact step-by-step directions to get you where you need to go.
